<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>üîç Pencarian Data Siswa Berdasarkan NISN</h1>
        <div class="search-section">
            <label for="nisnInput">Masukkan NISN:</label>
            <input type="text" id="nisnInput" placeholder="Contoh: 1234567890">
            <button id="searchButton">Cari Data</button>
        </div>
        <div id="loading" class="hidden">Memuat data...</div>
        <div id="result" class="result-section">
            </div>
        <button id="printPdfButton" class="hidden">Cetak PDF üñ®Ô∏è</button>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jspdf/2.5.1/jspdf.umd.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jspdf-autotable/3.5.25/jspdf.plugin.autotable.min.js"></script>

    <script>
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
            const nisnInput = document.getElementById('nisnInput');
            const searchButton = document.getElementById('searchButton');
            const resultDiv = document.getElementById('result');
            const loadingDiv = document.getElementById('loading');
            const printPdfButton = document.getElementById('printPdfButton');

            // GANTI DENGAN URL WEB APP ANDA DARI GOOGLE APPS SCRIPT
            const WEB_APP_URL = 'https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbwG9vtCrM8CV1kxjCWRFNedND_GJQ7gmICEM8uji7XtFRjqiznAML8s18LxCuRHhD4iRQ/exec'; // *** PASTIKAN INI DIGANTI ***

            // GANTI DENGAN URL LOGO SEKOLAH ANDA
            const LOGO_URL = 'data:image/png;base64,'; // *** PASTIKAN INI DIGANTI ***

            let currentStudentData = null; // To store data for PDF generation

            searchButton.addEventListener('click', fetchData);
            nisnInput.addEventListener('keypress', (event) => {
                if (event.key === 'Enter') {
                    fetchData();
                }
            });
            printPdfButton.addEventListener('click', printPdf);

            async function fetchData() {
                const nisn = nisnInput.value.trim();
                if (!nisn) {
                    resultDiv.innerHTML = '<p class="no-data">Mohon masukkan NISN untuk mencari data.</p>';
                    printPdfButton.classList.add('hidden');
                    return;
                }

                loadingDiv.classList.remove('hidden');
                resultDiv.innerHTML = ''; // Clear previous results
                printPdfButton.classList.add('hidden'); // Hide print button initially
                currentStudentData = null; // Clear previous data

                try {
                    const response = await fetch(`${WEB_APP_URL}?nisn=${nisn}`);
                    const data = await response.json();

                    loadingDiv.classList.add('hidden');

                    if (data && !data.error) {
                        currentStudentData = data; // Store the data
                        displayData(data);
                        printPdfButton.classList.remove('hidden');
                    } else {
                        resultDiv.innerHTML = `<p class="no-data">Data untuk NISN <strong>${nisn}</strong> tidak ditemukan. ${data.error ? '(' + data.error + ')' : ''}</p>`;
                        printPdfButton.classList.add('hidden');
                    }
                } catch (error) {
                    console.error('Error fetching data:', error);
                    loadingDiv.classList.add('hidden');
                    resultDiv.innerHTML = '<p class="no-data">Terjadi kesalahan saat mengambil data. Mohon coba lagi nanti.</p>';
                    printPdfButton.classList.add('hidden');
                }
            }

            function displayData(data) {
                let html = '<h2>Data Siswa Ditemukan:</h2>';
                html += '<p><strong>NISN:</strong> ' + (data['NISN'] || '-') + '</p>';
                html += '<p><strong>NAMA:</strong> ' + (data['NAMA'] || '-') + '</p>';
                html += '<p><strong>KELAS:</strong> ' + (data['KELAS'] || '-') + '</p>';
                html += '<p><strong>ALAMAT:</strong> ' + (data['ALAMAT'] || '-') + '</p>';
                html += '<p><strong>BIAYA SERAGAM:</strong> Rp ' + (formatRupiah(data['BIAYA SERAGAM']) || '-') + '</p>';
                html += '<p><strong>BIAYA KPS:</strong> Rp ' + (formatRupiah(data['BIAYA KPS']) || '-') + '</p>';
                html += '<p><strong>OUTING CLASS I:</strong> Rp ' + (formatRupiah(data['OUTING CLASS I']) || '-') + '</p>';
                html += '<p><strong>OUTING CLASS II:</strong> Rp ' + (formatRupiah(data['OUTING CLASS II']) || '-') + '</p>';
                html += '<p><strong>OUTING CLASS III:</strong> Rp ' + (formatRupiah(data['OUTING CLASS III']) || '-') + '</p>';
                html += '<p><strong>OUTING CLASS IV:</strong> Rp ' + (formatRupiah(data['OUTING CLASS IV']) || '-') + '</p>';
                html += '<p><strong>SALDO AWAL:</strong> Rp ' + (formatRupiah(data['SALDO AWAL']) || '-') + '</p>';
                html += '<p><strong>SISA SALDO:</strong> Rp ' + (formatRupiah(data['SISA SALDO']) || '-') + '</p>';
                resultDiv.innerHTML = html;
            }

            function formatRupiah(amount) {
                if (amount === undefined || amount === null || amount === '') {
                    return '0';
                }
                const numericAmount = parseFloat(amount);
                if (isNaN(numericAmount)) {
                    return amount;
                }
                return numericAmount.toLocaleString('id-ID');
            }

            function printPdf() {
                if (!currentStudentData) {
                    alert("Tidak ada data siswa untuk dicetak.");
                    return;
                }

                const { jsPDF } = window.jspdf;
                const doc = new jsPDF();

                // --- Bagian Kop Dokumen (Atas) dengan Logo ---
                const logoWidth = 23; // Atur lebar logo sesuai kebutuhan (dalam mm)
                const logoHeight = 23; // Atur tinggi logo sesuai kebutuhan (dalam mm)
                const logoX = 14;   // Posisi X logo dari kiri (dalam mm)
                const logoY = 15;   // Posisi Y logo dari atas (dalam mm)

                // Tambahkan gambar logo
                doc.addImage(LOGO_URL, 'PNG', logoX, logoY, logoWidth, logoHeight);

                const textX = logoX + logoWidth + 10; // Posisi X teks setelah logo
                const startYText = 15;

                doc.setFontSize(14);
                doc.text("LEMBAGA PENDIDIKAN ISLAM", textX, startYText, null, null, "left");
                doc.text("YAYASAN NURUL JANNAH SAWARAN LOR", textX, startYText + 7, null, null, "left");
                doc.setFontSize(16);
                doc.text("MTS NURUL JANNAH SAWARAN LOR", textX, startYText + 14, null, null, "left");
                doc.setFontSize(10);
                doc.text("Alamat: Jl. Gunnung Ringgit No 35 Desa Sawaran Lor e-mail: 085258867440", textX, startYText + 21, null, null, "left");
                doc.line(14, logoY + logoHeight + 5, 196, logoY + logoHeight + 5); // Garis pemisah setelah logo dan teks
                doc.line(14, logoY + logoHeight + 6, 196, logoY + logoHeight + 6); // Garis pemisah kedua

                doc.setFontSize(18);
                doc.text("Detail Data Siswa", 105, logoY + logoHeight + 20, null, null, "center"); // Posisikan judul di tengah

                doc.setFontSize(12);

                const data = [
                    ["NISN", currentStudentData['NISN'] || '-'],
                    ["NAMA", currentStudentData['NAMA'] || '-'],
                    ["KELAS", currentStudentData['KELAS'] || '-'],
                    ["ALAMAT", currentStudentData['ALAMAT'] || '-'],
                    ["BIAYA SERAGAM", "Rp " + (formatRupiah(currentStudentData['BIAYA SERAGAM']) || '-')],
                    ["BIAYA KPS", "Rp " + (formatRupiah(currentStudentData['BIAYA KPS']) || '-')],
                    ["OUTING CLASS I", "Rp " + (formatRupiah(currentStudentData['OUTING CLASS I']) || '-')],
                    ["OUTING CLASS II", "Rp " + (formatRupiah(currentStudentData['OUTING CLASS II']) || '-')],
                    ["OUTING CLASS III", "Rp " + (formatRupiah(currentStudentData['OUTING CLASS III']) || '-')],
                    ["OUTING CLASS IV", "Rp " + (formatRupiah(currentStudentData['OUTING CLASS IV']) || '-')],
                    ["SALDO AWAL", "Rp " + (formatRupiah(currentStudentData['SALDO AWAL']) || '-')],
                    ["SISA SALDO", "Rp " + (formatRupiah(currentStudentData['SISA SALDO']) || '-')]
                ];

                const startYTable = logoY + logoHeight + 30;

                doc.autoTable({
                    startY: startYTable,
                    head: [['Keterangan', 'Nilai']],
                    body: data,
                    theme: 'striped',
                    styles: {
                        font: 'helvetica',
                        fontSize: 10,
                        cellPadding: 3,
                        valign: 'middle',
                    },
                    headStyles: {
                        fillColor: [44, 62, 80],
                        textColor: [255, 255, 255],
                        fontStyle: 'bold'
                    },
                    altRowStyles: {
                        fillColor: [240, 240, 240]
                    },
                    columnStyles: {
                        0: { fontStyle: 'bold', cellWidth: 50 },
                        1: { cellWidth: 'auto' }
                    },
                    didDrawPage: function (data) {
                        // Anda bisa menambahkan footer multi-halaman di sini jika perlu
                    }
                });

                // --- Bagian Tanggal dan Nama Kepala Sekolah (Bawah) ---
                const finalY = doc.autoTable.previous.finalY;
                const marginX = 14;
                const pageWidth = doc.internal.pageSize.getWidth();

                const today = new Date();
                const options = { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' };
                const formattedDate = today.toLocaleDateString('id-ID', options);

                const kota = "Lumajang";
                const namaKepalaSekolah = "SAHRULLAH, S.Pd";
                const nipKepalaSekolah = "3508190405870003";

                doc.setFontSize(10);
                doc.text(`${kota}, ${formattedDate}`, pageWidth - marginX, finalY + 20, null, null, "right");
                doc.text("Kepala Sekolah,", pageWidth - marginX, finalY + 28, null, null, "right");
                doc.text("", pageWidth - marginX, finalY + 40, null, null, "right");
                doc.text(namaKepalaSekolah, pageWidth - marginX, finalY + 55, null, null, "right");
                doc.text(`NIP. ${nipKepalaSekolah}`, pageWidth - marginX, finalY + 60, null, null, "right");


                doc.save(`Data_Siswa_${currentStudentData['NISN'] || 'unknown'}.pdf`);
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
